</head>
<body>
  <header class="hero-section-babeshowerretgifts">
    <div class="hero-content-babeshowerretgifts fade-in-up-babeshowerretgifts">
      <h1>Charming Return Gifts for Guests</h1>
      <p>Send your guests home with a little love and appreciation — sweet, thoughtful, and unforgettable.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="gift-gallery-babeshowerretgifts fade-in-up-babeshowerretgifts">
    <h2>Return Gift Gallery</h2>
    <div class="grid-babeshowerretgifts">
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/soap gifts.jpeg" alt="Mini Soap Bars" />
        <h3>Handmade Soap Bars</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/candles gift.jpeg" alt="Custom Candle" />
        <h3>Mini Scented Candles</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/seed packets.jpeg" alt="Seed Packet Favor" />
        <h3>“Watch Me Grow” Seed Packets</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/honey jar.jpeg" alt="Honey Jar Favor" />
        <h3>Sweet Honey Jars</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/key chain.jpeg" alt="Baby Keychain" />
        <h3>Baby-Themed Keychains</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/bath bombs.jpeg" alt="Bath Bomb Gift" />
        <h3>Pastel Bath Bombs</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
        <img src="/img/cupcake jar.jpeg" alt="Cupcake Jar Favor" />
        <h3>Mini Cupcake Jars</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-babeshowerretgifts">
         <img src="/img/Succulent pot.jpeg" alt="Succulent Pot" />
         <h3>Mini Succulent Pots</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tips-box-babeshowerretgifts fade-in-up-babeshowerretgifts">
    <h2>Fiore’s Return Gifting Tips</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Choose favors that are practical yet charming — like candles, mini treats, or bath goodies.</li>
      <li>Add a personal touch with handwritten notes or tags.</li>
      <li>Stick to your theme — pastel wraps, floral patterns, or baby motifs go a long way.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

